	<p>VoiceTel respects your privacy. This policy complies with GDPR, CCPA/CPRA, and other applicable frameworks.</p>
	<h3>2. Data collection and use</h3>
	<p>Data is collected only for lawful, disclosed purposes. Processing is based on consent, contract, or legal obligation.</p>
