	<ul>
		<li>GDPR: rights of access, rectification, erasure, restriction, portability, and objection.</li>
		<li>CCPA/CPRA: rights to know, delete, correct, opt-out of sale/sharing.</li>
	</ul>
	<p>Requests must be submitted through designated channels.</p>
	<h3>4. Retention</h3>
	<p>Personal data is retained only as long as necessary for contractual or legal purposes.</p>
	<h3>5. Security</h3>
